This is a very simple script for make an automatic installation. This script have preconfigured directory to provide obarun with openbox booting S6, xfce4, plasma as desktop, but you can use it for install your own configuration.
Starting from obarun-iso or official Arch-iso or with a minimal Arch architecture is possible.
Own repository and AUR repo is supported.

Assumptions:
============

	User has partitioned, formatted, and mounted partitions on a directory
	Network is functional
	A valid mirror appears in /etc/pacman.d/mirrorlist

File description
================

You can find here http://wiki.obarun.org an explanation about structure/behaviour of the script.

